                "children": [
                    {
                        "editable": true,
                        "text": "Maintain a friendly and professional tone throughout the call."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "editable": true,
                "children": [
                    {
                        "editable": true,
                        "text": "Do not pressure the customer into sharing information."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "editable": true,
                "children": [
                    {
                        "editable": true,
                        "text": "Ensure all information is clear and concise."
